875
00:40:24,230 --> 00:40:25,120
I'll call him then.

876
00:40:31,910 --> 00:40:33,400
They're asking if you're coming.

877
00:40:41,710 --> 00:40:42,360
Is he coming?

878
00:40:42,800 --> 00:40:43,600
He's busy.

879
00:40:43,670 --> 00:40:44,880
Bai can't make it either.

880
00:40:44,880 --> 00:40:46,040
He has a date.

881
00:40:46,120 --> 00:40:47,750
What could he be busy with?

882
00:40:47,880 --> 00:40:48,880
Important matter.

883
00:40:52,670 --> 00:40:53,560
Let's eat.

884
00:40:53,840 --> 00:40:54,400
No one else is coming.

885
00:40:54,400 --> 00:40:55,400
So dig in.

886
00:40:55,640 --> 00:40:57,990
Since Dr. Ning isn't here,

887
00:40:58,160 --> 00:40:59,600
I'm going to tell you guys something.

888
00:41:00,470 --> 00:41:02,990
The seniors who used to work
at the hospital said

889
00:41:03,470 --> 00:41:06,080
Dr. Ning was married once.

890
00:41:07,670 --> 00:41:09,430
But he divorced after being married
for more than a year.

891
00:41:09,430 --> 00:41:10,840
He divorced after being married
for more than a year?

892
00:41:12,670 --> 00:41:14,990
Then who abandoned who?

893
00:41:15,270 --> 00:41:18,120
It must be Dr. Ning
who didn't want his ex-wife.

894
00:41:18,400 --> 00:41:19,510
How do you know?

895
00:41:20,190 --> 00:41:21,430
Think about it.

896
00:41:21,510 --> 00:41:23,840
Dr. Ning is a perfect man.

897
00:41:23,840 --> 00:41:25,880
